{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/example1.png?t=1738302100\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Background Setting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;52 Hertz&quot; is a <strong><i>futuristically apocalyptic Honkaku (authentic) mystery game</i></strong>. Trapped in a fog-shrouded, eerie town, you must work alongside the protagonist to solve murder cases and unmask the culprits. Through a series of puzzles, you'll seek out your own lost memories and uncover the truth about the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a future world, ShiMo, an explorer who has lost his childhood memories, arrives at a rumored anomaly - an enclosed town shrouded in thick fog - to uncover his origins and memories. However, on his very first night there, a murder occurs, serving only as the prelude to a series of events. As ShiMo builds connections with others, solving cases not only unravels the truth about the town but also leads him to the secrets of his own past and the lost memories that have haunted him...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/example2.png?t=1738302100\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the keyboard and mouse to control the character's movement, interactions, and puzzle-solving on a side-scrolling display.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/example3.png?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u64cd\u63a7\u4e0e\u5bfc\u822a.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u5bf9\u8bdd\uff08\u5934\u50cf\uff09.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Storyline Structure</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a storyline with multiple branching options, allowing players to explore various endings flexibly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u9009\u9879.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzle Design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's puzzles emphasize &quot;orthodox detection&quot; elements, designed based on the form of orthodox detection to create a classic plot structure akin to &quot;Ten Little Indians.&quot; They focus on clue collection and logical reasoning, enhancing the player's immersion and providing a direct experience of the pleasure of logical deduction while deeply engaging in the game's detective mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u975e\u65e5\u5e38\u8c03\u67e5.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u6392\u5e8f.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game includes systems such as notes, inventory, clues, and maps that serve the plot and facilitate the narrative and deduction aspects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/UI-\u7b14\u8bb0.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/UI-\u624b\u673a.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Art Style</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game employs a low saturation and washed-out style that combines 2D and 3D elements, creating a sense of subdued colors and fading tones. This visual approach conveys a tranquil yet melancholic atmosphere, offering a unique aesthetic experience within the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/\u5bf9\u8bdd.gif?t=1738302100\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Music Style</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game music consists of original compositions by Evalia-\u7231\u5a03\u3001\u6c89\u6797\u5ddd\u3001\u9ed1\u91d1\u96e8, and more. The original soundtrack will be available for purchase at a later date.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2964960?t=1738302100","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738302100","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738302100","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738302100","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2980040,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964960/extras/example1.png?t=1738302100\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Background Setting</